    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，这是一个循环结构吗？还是单向的？另外负载均衡器和缓存各需要几个节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_Cache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是循环结构，Worker最后要回到Ingress形成闭环。负载均衡器需要两个层级，缓存需要三个节点做分层。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_Worker",
        "Infra_Ingress",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_Cache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画主干：Ingress指向第一个LoadBalancer，然后串联第二个LoadBalancer，再到Cluster。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_Ingress",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_Cluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "前三个节点没问题。接下来从Cluster出来先到第一个Cache节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_Cluster",
        "Infra_Cache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加第一个Cache，继续串联第二个Cache。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_Cache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第二个Cache之后不是直接到第三个Cache，要先回到Cluster做一次处理，然后再进第三个Cache。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_Cache",
        "Infra_Cluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：第二个Cache → Cluster → 第三个Cache，是这样吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
